Show HN: Juicebox AI (YC S22), a hiring tool powered by GPT
text:
Hey HN,

We are experimenting with GPT-3.5 and applied it to hiring, helping with: resume summaries, interview questions, offer emails, and more.

See it in action: ai.juicebox.work (works best on Chrome). It’s free to use! We are continuing to fine-tune the models and improve the quality of output.

Feedback is appreciated, and happy to answer any questions :)

Ask HN: Have you run an accounting team for a marketplace?
text:
I am doing some discovery for an idea and wanted to see if anyone here has experience in running marketplaces?

I specifically want to know how did you guys think about financial reporting and payouts for your merchants. Did merchants ever complain about having to reconcile with your platform manually? Did you create QB or Xero plugins to help them?
